":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/14/120543_bf90b2dd4b6536be3763727986e7372e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F14%2F120543_bf90b2dd4b6536be3763727986e7372e.jpg&h=4c5ff49f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6ee63a2eba57c502cb532dc2b12dcd987b7c07c2","tid":321042,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T04:09:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有美國學者透露，印度已把核飛彈的瞄準目標，由巴基斯坦轉向中國。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊個美國學者咁巴閉，連核彈轉target都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果佢講到幾時射就最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c68181f1dcf8c63828d1164e9572f853d582ffab","tid":321042,"uid":41356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T05:01:45.000Z","msg":"點解烈火4同烈火5都係agni V"},{"pid":"508683cf4e05b2c4fe34cbc8c7deb2dea7e60f73","tid":321042,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T05:03:30.000Z","msg":"G持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb91fac2b0b3337662ec45b36d1e2b636349120f","tid":321042,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T05:39:13.000Z","msg":"你以為支那會驚咩<br />\n成個支那咁大 食你十零廿個都唔驚 射啦!"},{"pid":"bd317edfb22ce7de14eb73feab02d49b59f9a593","tid":321042,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T05:40:15.000Z","msg":"巴基斯坦心諗<br />\n原來仇家都唔夠大陸乞人憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}